{"tid":1615765,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十月四日，十二點半，遮打花園","createTime":"2019-10-03T07:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T03:36:37.000Z","uid":170812,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"789dbc408271420790b0c062c001526d73b711fc","tid":1615765,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:51:51.000Z","msg":"各位手足，十月二日嘅快閃中環遊行，有非常多人參與。其實不止中環，金鐘、灣仔、銅鑼灣甚至跑馬地，都有好多人出黎。期間，手足讀出簡短嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">中環宣言</span>，俾香港人睇到，中環價值並<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不止於經濟同金錢</span>，仲有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">良知同埋公義</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wkVdW_rzG14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwkVdW_rzG14&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGCNNnhsiPIcvur842Fp1uB0%3D&h=8a5d5d22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wkVdW_rzG14</a><br />\n<br />\n可惜，呢個暴政聽唔到我地嘅聲音。相隔僅僅一天，今日（十月三日）下午，更將中槍嘅少年同埋其他手足，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">控告暴動</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我希望聽日各位再次行出黎，與為我地擋子彈嘅手足同行。相比血、汗、青春、牢獄，我地少少嘅午飯時間，實在微不足道。<br />\n<br />\n期望藉著再一次午間遊行，可以為其他地區嘅手足豎立行動旗幟，一石激起千重浪！日後可能會有其他手足<span style=\"color: red;\">又再一次、兩次、三次</span>發起午間遊行，各位一定要<span style=\"color: red;\">堅持</span>行動，直至煲底相見！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十二點半</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遮打花園</span></span>見！"},{"pid":"473400a1e28f04bf421d4fb7a543f86ca78d0d12","tid":1615765,"uid":132999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:52:54.000Z","msg":"721 <br />\n831 <br />\n101"},{"pid":"a83b036aadac1a443194246bdd583e316507a1bb","tid":1615765,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:52:57.000Z","msg":"唔係附近返工幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694da24900d57aaee893cc0a894589dd2c54b808","tid":1615765,"uid":170812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:53:28.000Z","msg":"回顧十月二日的中環宣言：<br />\n<br />\n「各位市民好，我係一個中環返工既小小市民，香港之所以成功，係因為香港有一個完善既法律制度，公平公正公開咁審判，但依家呢個社會比我見到既只係一個警權無限大既社會，未審先判，對示威人士用過度既暴力，尋日十月一號既開槍事件，警察竟然將成個事件黑白顛倒，將打中左肺講成打中肩旁，我地香港人有既係智慧，有既係良知，絕對唔會接受大話連篇既政府、警隊統治同埋所謂守護我地既屋企<br />\n<br />\n中環宣言：<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可，<br />\n其中一定要實踐雙普選，鞏固我地香港核心價值，如果政府連呢啲民意都做唔到，中環，寧為玉碎，不作瓦全。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不止口講，我們還要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行動</span></span>！"},{"pid":"3d4d0b71466893ac0798e7e59ab374ded37703e0","tid":1615765,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"聽日，十二點半，遮打花園見！"},{"pid":"5b07ccf7244552f988a345118c0ce64a79fbcfda","tid":1615765,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:02:18.000Z","msg":"這個暴政，永遠不能原諒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JDZYbBi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJDZYbBi.jpg&h=8469771f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"843ab7f3dede95271550154dfbeee9d58af62232","tid":1615765,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"「寧為玉碎，不作瓦存」<br />\n<br />\n大家還記得嗎?"},{"pid":"b2c09a954ecac815ebf9845941848466344c3cb8","tid":1615765,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"為了所有人，即使只有丁點力量，也要盡做。<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n救健仔個邱義士原來讀緊博士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1615777\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1615777</a>"},{"pid":"dbf3e72f8fb1abf569e5eb03079dd1b82fb42758","tid":1615765,"uid":293507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:27:30.000Z","msg":"聽日，十二點半，遮打花園見！"},{"pid":"f215b4d0b9d7d3ae5f7883b10736831ae51b2078","tid":1615765,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:38:11.000Z","msg":"只係相隔一日，大家的心就已好過了?"},